Package edu.uiowa.cs.warp

Class ChannelVisualization

java.lang.Object
edu.uiowa.cs.warp.ChannelVisualization
public class ChannelVisualization extends Object
ChannelVisualization creates the visualizations for the channel analysis of the WARP program.

CS2820 Spring 2024 Project: Implement this class to create the file visualization that is requested in Warp.

Version:
1.7
Author:
